folder: Fingerboard Road (We & Richmond Road, Staten Island, NY
text:
W. Fingerboard Road, east side, 100 yards north of Richmond Road, showing (what Mr. Sperr calls) the Cameron House. In 1874 the house was owned by H. R. Baltzer; in 1898 by Mason; and from 1907 to 1917 by Charles Rosenberg and was called the "Beechwood."

May 20, 1926

P. L. Sperr

(2)

The same, at a later date.

May 24, 1932

P. L. Sperr
